775
00:31:31.170 --> 00:31:32.880
We really did.

776
00:31:32.880 --> 00:31:36.500
Look at that. Whoo!
[ Both laugh ]

777
00:31:36.500 --> 00:31:40.210
Oh... wow.

778
00:31:40.210 --> 00:31:43.170
Oh... nice.

779
00:31:43.170 --> 00:31:44.670
[ Chuckles ]

780
00:31:51.750 --> 00:31:54.000
Flowers, too? This is
