849
00:35:05.750 --> 00:35:08.080
[ Sighs ]

850
00:35:08.080 --> 00:35:10.750
Evening.

851
00:35:10.750 --> 00:35:12.750
What happened there?

852
00:35:12.750 --> 00:35:14.880
Oh. Kid with cancer.

853
00:35:14.880 --> 00:35:17.670
[ Telephone rings ]

854
00:35:17.670 --> 00:35:19.420
[ Chuckles ]

855
00:35:19.420 --> 00:35:25.420
