919
00:38:18.420 --> 00:38:20.750
I can't teach you
how to do this.

920
00:38:20.750 --> 00:38:22.210
I'm sorry.

921
00:38:22.210 --> 00:38:23.790
[ Elevator bell dings,
doors open ]

922
00:38:23.790 --> 00:38:25.500
But I, uh...

