00:38:25.500 --> 00:38:27.080
[ Indistinct conversations ]

924
00:38:27.080 --> 00:38:28.830
I thought this was
a teaching hospital!

925
00:38:32.710 --> 00:38:36.000
Look, I'm sorry I went
against your chief-ness,

